WEBVTT

00:02.042 --> 00:02.958
NARRATOR:
Throughout the ancient world,

00:03.083 --> 00:05.583
there were tales of mortals

00:05.708 --> 00:07.208
and immortals.

00:07.333 --> 00:08.917
AMIR HUSSAIN:
In Christian traditions,

00:09.042 --> 00:10.375
in Islamic traditions,

00:10.542 --> 00:12.000
and Hindu traditions,

00:12.125 --> 00:14.333
you have these divine beings
who live forever.

00:14.417 --> 00:18.333
NARRATOR:
Could these stories be
accounts of alien visitors

00:18.458 --> 00:22.500
who traveled to Earth from
thousands of lightyears away?

00:22.625 --> 00:25.250
TRAVIS TAYLOR:
Imagine an advanced civilization

00:25.375 --> 00:27.167
that has interstellar travel.

00:27.333 --> 00:30.500
If they can travel
through the stars, they could

00:30.583 --> 00:33.875
stretch their longevity
maybe even to centuries.

00:34.042 --> 00:36.750
NARRATOR:
And if humans are to one day

00:36.875 --> 00:38.208
colonize other planets,

00:38.333 --> 00:40.167
will we too need to discover

00:40.250 --> 00:42.750
the key to immortality?

00:42.875 --> 00:45.042
DAVID CHILDRESS:
What our extraterrestrial
ancestors

00:45.208 --> 00:46.792
have wanted us to do

00:46.875 --> 00:49.167
is be like them.

00:49.292 --> 00:52.458
They want us to be a spacefaring
race that goes to the stars.

00:52.542 --> 00:55.875
And to live
these extended lives where

00:56.042 --> 00:58.083
we become essentially immortal.

01:01.042 --> 01:02.750
NARRATOR:
There is a doorway

01:02.875 --> 01:05.458
in the universe.

01:05.542 --> 01:08.667
Beyond it is
the promise of truth.

01:09.958 --> 01:12.542
It demands
we question everything

01:12.667 --> 01:15.000
we have ever been taught.

01:15.125 --> 01:18.458
The evidence is all around us.

01:18.583 --> 01:22.500
The future is
right before our eyes.

01:22.625 --> 01:25.208
We are not alone.

01:25.333 --> 01:28.458
We have never been alone.

01:38.667 --> 01:42.125
The Ashmolean Museum
of art and archaeology.

01:43.375 --> 01:46.833
Among the hundreds of
historic artifacts on display

01:46.958 --> 01:50.000
is an ancient
Sumerian cuneiform text.

01:50.125 --> 01:53.500
Dating back to at least
2000 BC,

01:53.667 --> 01:57.292
the four-sided clay document
is a list of kings

01:57.375 --> 02:01.083
who lived far longer than
the average human life span.

02:02.375 --> 02:04.667
In the Ashmolean Museum
at Oxford,

02:04.833 --> 02:06.333
there's an astounding artifact.

02:06.417 --> 02:08.917
It's referred to as WB44,

02:09.042 --> 02:10.750
the Sumerian Kings List.

02:12.417 --> 02:15.792
On one panel, it tells us
about eight kings

02:15.917 --> 02:19.458
that ruled over five cities, and
what's astounding about this

02:19.583 --> 02:22.542
is the length of
the reigns of these kings.

02:22.708 --> 02:27.167
One king is said to have ruled
for 43,200 years.

02:27.292 --> 02:30.917
Another king rules
for 28,000 years.

02:31.042 --> 02:32.458
It's astounding.

02:33.542 --> 02:36.333
NARRATOR:
Curiously,
the Sumerian Kings List

02:36.458 --> 02:38.833
is not the only
ancient record of rulers

02:38.958 --> 02:41.167
who lived for centuries.

02:41.292 --> 02:44.667
A curious document
was found in a tomb

02:44.792 --> 02:46.333
in Luxor,

02:46.458 --> 02:49.750
and it's called the, uh,
Turin Kings List.

02:51.583 --> 02:54.708
We only have fragments
of this document,

02:54.875 --> 02:57.333
but what this document lays out

02:57.500 --> 03:00.417
is that many of the really early

03:00.542 --> 03:03.333
Egyptian pharaohs had lives

03:03.458 --> 03:06.042
that were many
hundreds of years,

03:06.208 --> 03:09.083
and that some
of these pharaohs lived

03:09.208 --> 03:12.417
for 700, 800, 900 years.

03:13.583 --> 03:17.292
We have a similar story
in the Bible of Methuselah

03:17.417 --> 03:19.042
and that he's said to have lived

03:19.167 --> 03:22.500
for 969 years.

03:22.583 --> 03:26.167
So, how is it that
people are able

03:26.292 --> 03:29.250
to live such great ages?

03:30.708 --> 03:32.583
NARRATOR:
Is it merely coincidence

03:32.708 --> 03:35.542
that in three different
ancient traditions

03:35.667 --> 03:37.958
there are records
of their earliest leaders

03:38.083 --> 03:40.333
living impossibly long lives?

03:41.208 --> 03:45.167
Curiously,
in all three cultures, it was

03:45.292 --> 03:48.208
also recorded that, during
the time when people lived

03:48.375 --> 03:51.500
to these incredible ages,
humans shared the Earth

03:51.667 --> 03:54.542
with beings who came down
from the sky.

03:56.083 --> 03:58.083
The ancient Egyptians
referred to

03:58.208 --> 04:00.500
a-a time called the first time,

04:00.625 --> 04:03.708
when the gods walked among men.

04:04.958 --> 04:08.500
Ancient Egyptian creation
mythology tells us that these

04:08.583 --> 04:12.583
original god beings
came from the stars.

04:12.708 --> 04:15.250
This sounds very much like
the arrival of the Anunnaki,

04:15.375 --> 04:18.500
the divine lords of light
of the Sumerian tradition

04:18.583 --> 04:22.417
when they arrived
atop Mount Kerzok.

04:22.542 --> 04:25.500
It's also virtually identical
to the arrival of the Watchers.

04:25.625 --> 04:29.208
The Watchers are the angels

04:29.333 --> 04:31.000
of the Old Testament.

04:31.125 --> 04:34.125
They are the fallen angels

04:34.208 --> 04:35.500
who came to Earth

04:35.625 --> 04:38.000
and intermingled with humans.

04:41.167 --> 04:43.208
NARRATOR:
The Watchers, like divine beings

04:43.375 --> 04:45.292
in many other ancient cultures,

04:45.375 --> 04:48.667
were referred to as immortals,
but often

04:48.750 --> 04:52.458
they were described as having
very humanlike traits.

04:53.292 --> 04:55.167
There were 200
of these Watchers,

04:55.250 --> 04:57.500
and they were led by, uh,

04:57.667 --> 04:59.667
an individual named Samyaza.

04:59.792 --> 05:01.833
They shone.

05:01.917 --> 05:03.667
There was a translucence.

05:03.792 --> 05:07.333
There was an aura about them
that was as bright as the Sun.

05:07.500 --> 05:11.250
But they seem to be more human
in their appetites

05:11.375 --> 05:13.917
than one would like to believe.

05:14.042 --> 05:15.417
They're hungry, they eat,

05:15.542 --> 05:17.375
they want affection, they lust.

05:18.708 --> 05:22.250
I think that the Watchers
most definitely

05:22.375 --> 05:25.167
are extraterrestrials
who came to Earth.

05:25.333 --> 05:28.875
Countless ancient,
original cultures

05:29.042 --> 05:32.000
speak of a time when the gods

05:32.125 --> 05:33.833
descended from the sky

05:33.917 --> 05:37.500
and mingled with people
to impart their knowledge.

05:38.500 --> 05:39.917
Ancient Egypt,

05:40.042 --> 05:41.708
ancient China,

05:41.833 --> 05:43.375
ancient Sumeria,

05:43.500 --> 05:45.083
ancient Japan,

05:45.208 --> 05:47.083
ancient Greece.

05:47.208 --> 05:49.333
And so, I think
the different cultures

05:49.458 --> 05:52.167
were visited
by the same teachers,

05:52.250 --> 05:53.500
who were extraterrestrials.

05:53.583 --> 05:55.500
NARRATOR:
Could it be

05:55.625 --> 05:58.000
that the earliest
human civilizations

05:58.083 --> 06:01.625
shared the Earth with visitors
from another world?

06:01.750 --> 06:02.917
And if so,

06:03.042 --> 06:05.667
is this somehow connected
to the ancient records

06:05.792 --> 06:09.708
of people who lived
extraordinarily long lives?

06:10.833 --> 06:14.167
Ancient astronaut theorists
suggest an important clue

06:14.292 --> 06:16.458
can be found in a famous verse

06:16.542 --> 06:19.667
from the Bible that
is often mistranslated.

06:19.792 --> 06:22.625
In many English versions
of the Book of Genesis,

06:22.750 --> 06:25.458
chapter one, verse 27 states

06:25.542 --> 06:28.958
that "God created man
in his own image."

06:29.083 --> 06:30.958
But in the original Hebrew,

06:31.083 --> 06:34.667
instead of "his" image,
it says "our" image.

06:35.708 --> 06:39.500
God says in Genesis,
"Let us make man in our image."

06:39.583 --> 06:41.792
Well, you have to say,
"Well, who is 'our'?

06:41.917 --> 06:43.625
Who-who are the
other people there?"

06:44.708 --> 06:48.500
Well, the word "God"
in Hebrew is "Elohim,"

06:48.625 --> 06:51.000
and that is plural.

06:51.125 --> 06:53.833
TSOUKALOS:
If you look at
the original Hebrew

06:53.958 --> 06:56.458
in which the sentence
was written,

06:56.542 --> 06:59.667
all of a sudden
you have the truth

06:59.750 --> 07:02.542
because, according to
the ancient astronaut theory,

07:02.667 --> 07:06.000
someone came
and someone altered our DNA

07:06.125 --> 07:07.792
in order for us

07:07.875 --> 07:09.333
to become humans

07:09.458 --> 07:12.875
and essentially gave us
more intelligence.

07:14.708 --> 07:16.583
ERICH VON DÄNIKEN:
Practically every culture,

07:16.708 --> 07:19.333
including our Bible, says,
"In the beginning,

07:19.500 --> 07:21.417
God," in the plurals, "created

07:21.542 --> 07:25.292
humans according
their own image."

07:25.417 --> 07:27.250
I'm a deep believer in God,

07:27.375 --> 07:29.667
but God is something gigantic,

07:29.792 --> 07:32.333
spiritual, not explainable.

07:32.458 --> 07:35.333
In my opinion,
when you read the Bible,

07:35.458 --> 07:38.667
it's all about
extraterrestrials.

07:38.792 --> 07:40.667
Part of ancient astronaut theory

07:40.750 --> 07:44.042
is that what
our extraterrestrial

07:44.208 --> 07:46.292
ancestors have wanted us to do

07:46.375 --> 07:48.167
is be like them.

07:49.667 --> 07:51.542
They want us to achieve

07:51.708 --> 07:54.458
the same things
that they achieved.

07:55.333 --> 07:58.500
The goal was,
some thousands of years

07:58.667 --> 08:00.208
in the far future,

08:00.375 --> 08:03.875
this humanity should be able
to construct spaceships

08:04.000 --> 08:06.583
to spread out
in the universe again.

08:10.208 --> 08:13.500
NARRATOR:
If <i>Homo sapiens</i> were
genetically engineered

08:13.583 --> 08:15.667
by extraterrestrial
space travelers

08:15.833 --> 08:17.500
to one day become like them

08:17.625 --> 08:20.250
and seed life on other planets,

08:20.375 --> 08:24.167
what might this mean for
the future of the human race?

08:24.250 --> 08:28.333
Some experts have suggested
that interstellar travel

08:28.417 --> 08:31.833
will only be possible
when science finds a way

08:31.958 --> 08:35.458
to dramatically extend
the human life span.

08:35.542 --> 08:37.750
TAYLOR:
Maybe our generation,

08:37.875 --> 08:39.750
with new developments
in technologies,

08:39.875 --> 08:42.792
will be living
to the mid-100s, 150,

08:42.875 --> 08:45.667
maybe even up to 200
in the next few decades.

08:45.792 --> 08:48.750
So, imagine
an advanced civilization

08:48.875 --> 08:51.000
that has interstellar travel.

08:51.125 --> 08:53.917
Certainly, if they can travel
through the stars,

08:54.042 --> 08:57.583
they could stretch
their longevity

08:57.708 --> 08:59.750
maybe even to centuries.

09:01.542 --> 09:04.458
NARRATOR:
Could it be that
the ancient people

09:04.542 --> 09:06.542
referred to the gods
as "immortals"

09:06.708 --> 09:08.667
because they encountered
space travelers

09:08.792 --> 09:11.042
who lived
for thousands of years?

09:11.208 --> 09:13.208
And if so,

09:13.375 --> 09:15.333
is it possible
that there are records

09:15.500 --> 09:17.833
of early rulers
living for centuries

09:18.000 --> 09:22.167
because these visitors somehow
extended their life spans?

09:23.250 --> 09:26.167
RABBI ARIEL BAR TZADOK:
It was natural for people

09:26.250 --> 09:27.792
in those days

09:27.875 --> 09:31.792
to live a life close
to a thousand years,

09:31.875 --> 09:35.292
but we're talking
about those who interacted

09:35.375 --> 09:38.583
with these beings
from the stars.

09:38.708 --> 09:41.500
Are these things connected?

09:41.625 --> 09:44.667
HENRY:
We're talking about an age
in which otherworldly beings

09:44.833 --> 09:47.167
assist humankind in becoming

09:47.292 --> 09:50.000
very much like the gods.

09:51.208 --> 09:54.667
NARRATOR:
But if our ancestors
from deep antiquity

09:54.833 --> 09:58.750
were so close to becoming like
their extraterrestrial creators,

09:58.875 --> 10:01.542
as ancient astronaut
theorists suggest,

10:01.708 --> 10:05.083
what kept them
from realizing this destiny?

10:05.208 --> 10:08.792
And are humans today
still on the same path?

10:08.917 --> 10:11.208
Perhaps further clues
can be found

10:11.333 --> 10:14.292
by examining a story
shared by different cultures

10:14.417 --> 10:16.167
all over the world,

10:16.333 --> 10:19.000
the story of the Great Flood.

10:24.042 --> 10:26.292
NARRATOR:
The Bible's Book of Genesis.

10:26.375 --> 10:28.875
In chapter six, verse nine

10:29.000 --> 10:31.667
begins the story of Noah
and the flood,

10:31.792 --> 10:35.125
in which God
sends a great deluge

10:35.250 --> 10:39.000
to cleanse the Earth,
which has become overrun by sin.

10:40.042 --> 10:43.042
It is one of the most
well-known tales from the Bible,

10:43.167 --> 10:46.542
but, curiously,
nearly identical stories

10:46.708 --> 10:49.958
exist in dozens of
other ancient traditions.

10:50.875 --> 10:53.667
BILL BIRNES:
We've heard about
the flood of Noah,

10:53.792 --> 10:56.833
which wiped out that
whole generation and brought

10:56.917 --> 11:00.083
about a new generation
of descendants of Noah.

11:00.208 --> 11:01.542
The fact is,

11:01.667 --> 11:04.667
there's all these stories
of the Great Flood

11:04.750 --> 11:07.042
in all countries
across the world.

11:08.042 --> 11:10.833
Plato talked about Atlantis.

11:10.917 --> 11:13.667
He talked about
a whole civilization

11:13.750 --> 11:16.333
destroyed by floods.

11:16.417 --> 11:17.500
In the Bible,

11:17.625 --> 11:20.333
Turkey, in Egypt,

11:20.458 --> 11:22.250
among the Native Americans,

11:22.375 --> 11:24.000
there's a story

11:24.125 --> 11:27.417
that the Great Flood wrapped
around the entire planet.

11:27.542 --> 11:29.750
All life was destroyed.

11:29.875 --> 11:31.750
The connection between
the biblical story

11:31.875 --> 11:34.875
of the Great Flood
and the destruction

11:35.000 --> 11:38.917
of other societies
around the world

11:39.042 --> 11:41.708
through floods
tell us one thing.

11:41.875 --> 11:43.542
There actually was
a Great Flood

11:43.667 --> 11:46.000
and that, at one point

11:46.125 --> 11:47.833
in the history of this planet,

11:47.958 --> 11:50.167
all life was wiped out

11:50.292 --> 11:54.250
as the Earth
was covered in water.

11:56.208 --> 11:58.833
VON DÄNIKEN:
In all mythologies,
including the Bible,

11:59.000 --> 12:01.000
some gods are coming down

12:01.083 --> 12:03.500
and teach the human
a great flood

12:03.625 --> 12:04.875
will come and destroy you.

12:05.042 --> 12:08.708
And these god,
they knew it long before,

12:08.833 --> 12:11.000
and they knew it because

12:11.125 --> 12:14.083
they themselves
made the Great Flood.

12:15.250 --> 12:19.417
The Great Flood was created
by extraterrestrials on purpose.

12:20.542 --> 12:22.792
NARRATOR:
Could the story
of the Great Flood

12:22.875 --> 12:25.125
be a historical record
of a real event

12:25.208 --> 12:28.667
that was brought on
by extraterrestrials?

12:28.792 --> 12:32.125
But if the ancient
astronaut theory is correct,

12:32.208 --> 12:36.167
and aliens genetically
engineered humankind,

12:36.292 --> 12:39.750
why would they then destroy
their greatest creation?

12:41.208 --> 12:44.500
TZADOK:
We have the records, as
described in the Book of Enoch

12:44.625 --> 12:46.000
and other literature,

12:46.125 --> 12:49.167
that the Watchers led
to the moral corruption

12:49.333 --> 12:51.000
of all humanity,

12:51.125 --> 12:54.375
which led to the destruction
of the face of the Earth.

12:54.542 --> 12:58.042
They were introducing
hidden technologies

12:58.167 --> 13:01.000
centuries before they were meant
to be introduced.

13:01.125 --> 13:03.833
They corrupted
the human gene pool.

13:03.958 --> 13:06.667
CARTER:
In Genesis six,

13:06.750 --> 13:08.917
we hear about the sons of God.

13:09.042 --> 13:11.167
They see the daughters of men,

13:11.292 --> 13:14.042
and they lust after them,
and they come down,

13:14.167 --> 13:17.500
and they take them as wives.

13:17.625 --> 13:21.542
And then they create a hybrid
race called the Nephilim.

13:21.708 --> 13:25.167
You weren't supposed to
fraternize with the natives,

13:25.250 --> 13:28.667
but this is what we
are told in the Bible.

13:28.792 --> 13:30.875
Now, what are we to make
of these texts?

13:31.042 --> 13:33.708
Are we to say,
"Well, maybe these angels,

13:33.833 --> 13:35.375
"these sons of God,
did they have sex

13:35.500 --> 13:37.000
the old-fashioned way?"

13:37.125 --> 13:39.167
We don't know,
but we need to start

13:39.292 --> 13:43.583
looking at these stories
from a 21st century perspective.

13:44.625 --> 13:48.583
With the technology that
we have with genetic engineering

13:48.708 --> 13:50.292
and splicing genes
and what have you,

13:50.417 --> 13:53.167
maybe we can revisit
this story and look

13:53.250 --> 13:55.833
at it from maybe
an extraterrestrial,

13:56.000 --> 13:57.917
uh, hypothesis or point of view.

13:58.042 --> 14:01.208
They're creating a hybrid race.

14:01.333 --> 14:04.250
The DNA of the
off-world intelligence

14:04.375 --> 14:05.708
and the human DNA

14:05.875 --> 14:08.167
creates this hybrid race,
and most

14:08.333 --> 14:11.750
of these beings,
for better or for worse,

14:11.875 --> 14:15.000
had what we could call
superhuman powers.

14:16.208 --> 14:18.333
NARRATOR:
As far as ancient
astronaut theorists

14:18.458 --> 14:22.000
are concerned,
a genetic upgrade occurred.

14:22.083 --> 14:26.000
One that closed the gap
between mortals and immortals

14:26.083 --> 14:28.333
far more quickly
than was intended.

14:28.417 --> 14:31.708
And it is a story that,
once again,

14:31.833 --> 14:34.500
was told across many cultures.

14:35.458 --> 14:38.125
When the sons of God
procreated with

14:38.208 --> 14:39.833
the daughters of men,
it is said that

14:40.000 --> 14:42.833
mighty ones were born.

14:42.958 --> 14:45.833
They had a longer
life span as well,

14:45.917 --> 14:47.792
dating maybe centuries,

14:47.917 --> 14:50.333
up to a thousand years--
not immortal

14:50.417 --> 14:53.875
but a life span much,
much longer than ours.

14:55.500 --> 14:58.208
CHILDRESS:
When you look back at
ancient Egyptian history,

14:58.333 --> 15:01.542
the pharaohs themselves
were said to be demigods.

15:03.125 --> 15:06.000
Part-god, part-human.

15:06.083 --> 15:09.167
JONATHAN YOUNG:
This was present
in the Greek imagination.

15:09.292 --> 15:12.125
The Olympians were known
to get involved in the world

15:12.250 --> 15:14.375
of the mortals, and they
would intervene sometimes.

15:14.542 --> 15:17.083
Sometimes they would
get attracted to a mortal

15:17.208 --> 15:19.667
and children would come.
Hercules, Perseus.

15:19.792 --> 15:23.542
These are the offspring,
demigods, half-god, half-human.

15:23.708 --> 15:26.667
NARRATOR:
But in many
of the ancient stories,

15:26.833 --> 15:30.375
the gods who were responsible
for this upgrade of humanity

15:30.500 --> 15:34.042
were acting against the wishes
of their superiors.

15:34.167 --> 15:37.958
They were not just helping
to jumpstart human civilization

15:38.083 --> 15:41.500
but creating
a new race of immortals.

15:41.583 --> 15:45.292
CARTER:
Enoch, who's the scribe of God,

15:45.417 --> 15:49.333
says that these angels
went against the will of God.

15:49.458 --> 15:52.792
Now, you can imagine
those angels were

15:52.875 --> 15:55.167
extraterrestrial in origin.

15:55.333 --> 15:57.833
If there was a prime directive,
they violated it.

15:57.958 --> 16:00.250
They gave us gifts,

16:00.375 --> 16:03.583
and we weren't ready
for those gifts.

16:03.708 --> 16:05.917
It's like giving
a gun to a baby.

16:06.042 --> 16:07.292
Nothing good will happen.

